messages.message:
@Aaron Tami @Jonathan Shih RBS is facing some inconsistent behaviour with process files. For the same set of input files, the results are not consistent. A file that was processed successfully in previous run was failing with current run.

They are running on 8/27 build. We have seen similar issue before with our production and it has been reported.

Whether this issue will get fixed if we ship the latest release?

CC: @Kerry @Matt
